Twenty-eighth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 6 
</p>
<p><b>Universal periodic review 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Working Group on the Universal Periodic 
Review</b>*<b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Slovenia 
</b></p>
<p>  
</p>
<p> 
* 
</p>
<p>The annex to the present report is circulated as received. 
</p>

<p>Contents 
</p>
<p><i> Paragraphs Page</i> 
</p>
