</b></p>
<p><b>of the majority of the population (Austria);  
</b></p>
<p>115.92 <b>Harmonize the rights of homosexual couples with those of 
</b></p>
<p><b>heterosexual couples (Spain);  
</b></p>
<p>115.93 <b>Heed the call by the Committee on the Rights of the Child to 
</b></p>
