</b></p>
<p><b>Great Britain and Northern Ireland);  
</b></p>
<p>115.95 <b>Enact comprehensive legislation addressing the situation of the 
</b></p>
<p>&#8220;<b>erased</b>&#8221;<b>, ensuring them appropriate assistance and protection (Uruguay);  
</b></p>
<p>115.96 Immediately restitute permanent residence for the &#8220;erased&#8221; persons 
</p>
<p><b>and adequately compensate them (Venezuela (Bolivarian Republic of));  </b></p>


<p>115.97 <b>Recognize fully the civil and political rights of </b>&#8220;<b>erased</b>&#8221;<b> citizens and 
