<p>115.101 <b>That the youth guarantee scheme is implemented without 
</b></p>
<p><b>discrimination and sufficient budget allocated for its effective implementation 
</b></p>
<p><b>(India);  
</b></p>
<p>115.102 <b>Take comprehensive measures to protect the rights of all national 
