</b></p>
<p><i>[English only] 
</i></p>
<p><b>  Composition of the delegation 
</b></p>
<p>The delegation of Slovenia was headed by H.E. Mr. Goran Klemen&#269;i&#269;, Minister of 
</p>
<p>Justice and composed of the following members: 
</p>
<p>&#8226; H.E. Mr. Bogdan Benko, Ambassador, State Secretary, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 
Deputy Head of Delegation; 
</p>
<p>&#8226; Mr. Stanko Baluh, Acting Director, Office of the Government of the Republic of 
